    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For now I have no nice way to handle that.\n\nSo :\n- I created a second helper that just do an empty query if no results are found in the first helper\n- Re-display only the facet block and adding a empty class on each facet refinements\n- When I click on a facet if an empty class is here, I set the query to \"\"\n\nThat's why I ask for algolia/algoliasearch-helper-js#146 to avoid this double helper.\n",
