    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "It's fairly easy to implement, just tried it with refinement list, it's working well. \nOne thing to note is that it needs autoHide to be true to have a good experience\n\nFor reference this is the code needed to do it\n\n```\nif (facetValues.length === 0) {\n        facetValues = helper.getRefinements(facetName).map(function(facet) {\n          return {\n            count: 0,\n            isRefined: true,\n            name: facet.value,\n            url: //fixme\n          };\n        });\n      }\n```\n",
